text: Ancenis-Saint-Géréon is a commune in the department of Loire-Atlantique. It was established on 1 January 2019 from the amalgamation of the communes of Ancenis and Saint-Géréon. ==References== Category:Communes of Loire-Atlantique Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Ancenis-Saint-Géréon
